{"type": "article", "id": 19612, "title": "动物钥匙圈", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-24T07:40:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135555SPsDa62wgUujd4Hp.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是由台湾的设计团队 Desk+1 做的一组动物钥匙圈，有兔子、狗和猫三种。不同于市面上挂动物吊坠的做法，他们用 304 不锈钢打磨出动物的轮廓，可以直接当做钥匙圈使用，简单而精巧。旁边连上一根真皮带，让钥匙圈有了质感。目前正在众筹，<a href=\"http://www.zeczec.com/projects/340\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135553yglfR6osiIqahMrQ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135554QMcCiV9ne7Ro608w.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135554q20dDmeuGjlV5tZ6.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135555qhmb0eiDna2GEOBt.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}